    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Note that rescanning for information has traditionally been carried out on receipt of a signal in unix land  (commonly SIGHUP); having a user-initiated rescan will cut down on the amount of unnecessary work the validator has to do.\r\n\r\nPerhaps this could be an RPC call in to the validator (if the validator even has an RPC interface)?",
